%N A385021 Number of states in smallest Fibonacci DFAO generating the sequence A003849(n*i).
%C A385021 A Fibonacci DFAO is a finite automaton that takes an integer input i represented in Fibonacci (aka Zeckendorf) representation and gives an output (associated with the last state reached).
%H A385021 Delaram Moradi, <a href="https://hdl.handle.net/10012/23044">State Complexity of Linear Relations and Linear Subsequences of Automatic Sequences</a>, Master's Thesis, Univ. Waterloo (Ontario, Canada, 2026). See p. 71.
